<div id="content">
  <DIV id="home-about">
  <DIV style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; color: #000000;">
  Forster Drilling is engaged in three related business activities:
  <DIV style="color: white; line-height: 1.8;">
    <UL>
      <LI>
	Providing contract land drilling services to oil and gas exploration
	and production companies.
      <LI>
        Building new rigs by fabricating components and assembling them 
with  
        new or rebuilt OEM components into state-of-the-art rotary drilling rigs.
      <LI>
	Exploration, development, production and sale of oil and natural 
gas.
    </UL>
  </DIV>
    As a drilling contractor, the Forster family has a reputation for reliability,
    high-quality equipment, and well-trained crews spanning three-quarters of
    a century.
</DIV>
